title: RimWorld Alpha version 6 (LINUX/WINDOWS/OSX)
description:
A sci-fi colony sim driven by an intelligent AI storyteller.

RimWorld follows three survivors from a crashed space liner as they build a colony on a frontier world at the rim of the galaxy.
		
Version 6 Woohoooooo! Biomes, and a new medical system. New update for your face. Have fun, enjoy, and remember this. You will die alone and ugly if you don't buy the game eventually. :D
